{"tid":1533210,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[長期置項]全世界開post果陣麻煩喺標題到加返\"9月3全港三罷\"喺尾","createTime":"2019-09-02T16:34:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T07:40:35.000Z","uid":83993,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0dcb98ee8e4620c426503db654d8fffc5f8caf26","tid":1533210,"uid":83993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:34:49.000Z","msg":"好多人都覺得今日9月2 罷工完全唔夠討論<br />\n我明白大部份人焦點都係喺即時討論 或者衝突/暴力畫面 搞到好多幾日既行動post完全推唔郁<br />\n<br />\n不過解決方法好簡單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n就係請大家開post果陣麻煩加返 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">&quot;9月3全港三罷&quot;</span></span>喺尾<br />\n再加埋 一段仔文字去宣傳全港三罷 好似呂麗乳搖巴一樣 加返段細細段 論壇簽名一樣<br />\n一定要加埋集中討論post條link 我覺得每個活動都可以come up一個template比大家去跟 <br />\n其他和理非行動例如逢星期五日罷買 或者 杯葛TVB 廣告都可以照樣咁做<br />\n咁樣大家可以集中地區行動時 又可以順便宣傳埋其他和理非行動 就唔洗驚宣傳度唔夠啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5650c9316336ab2086f1a7f7175e08d7dd4e719a","tid":1533210,"uid":83993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:35:50.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59efb4682830e2e1214616fde898340157b3668b","tid":1533210,"uid":83993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:37:39.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebea4cd1f5990fb1ba6cf8d425809550ec5c9bcf","tid":1533210,"uid":83993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:37:49.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"